The '''MG3''' was a [[Krupx Munitions/Legends|Krupx]] mini-missile tube developed for use by groundships and [[Repulsorlift/Legends|speeders]]. [[Turbostorm-class gunship|''Turbostorm''-class gunships]] were equipped with two MG3 tubes, for the fore and aft. Each MG3 tube carried two launchers, each which could fire one missile a second and had a magazine of four missiles.

